		<div class="columns">
			<h1>Networking at the LendIt Conference</h1>
			<section>
				<p>LendIt is the perfect opportunity to get to know leaders and newcomers alike in the marketplace lending industry. We want to help you take full advantage of the unique opportunity to network in person with other attendees and companies. Between our dedicated LendIt mobile app and LendIt staff, we can help you make the most of LendIt USA 2015.</p>

				<p>So here are the top 10 ways to network at LendIt:</p>
			</section>
		</div>
		<div class="columns">
			<ol reversed="reversed" start="10">

				<li>Prepare early. Figure out who you want to meet and ask your friends for intros.</li>

				<li>Hit the exhibit hall and share the QR code on the back of your name badge.</li>

				<li>Request meetings with companies hosting private meeting rooms on the 7th floor.</li>

				<li>Exhibitors, Silver, Bronze, and Associate Sponsors: talk to our Sales Director, <a href="mailto:bladimir@lendit.co">Bladimir Estevez</a>.</li>

				<li>Speakers, Title, Platinum, and Gold Sponsorship: contact <a href="mailto:lisa@lendit.co">Lisa Jones</a>, Director of Delegate Affairs, for LendIt's Concierge Networking services.</li>

				<li>Check out our <a href="/attendees">global visualization</a> to search for companies by country.</li>

				<li>Look up speakers on the <a href="/speakers">LendIt Speakers page</a> and connect on LinkedIn.</li>

				<li>Download the <a href="/attendees">list of companies attending</a> and connect on LinkedIn.</li>

				<li>Check out the attendee list and message other attendees through the <a href="https://event.crowdcompass.com/lendit-usa-2015" target="_blank">LendIt mobile networking app</a>; It can be found on <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewSoftware?id=858490125&mt=8" target="_blank">Itunes</a> and <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.crowdcompass.app4PWcdwDO6j" target="_blank">Google Play</a>.</li>

				<li>Interact! Get there early and stay late. Maximize your time by attending all of the events around LendIt.</li>



